data.description: We are thrilled to present this 4 bedroom, 2 bath, single-family home located in the thriving Harris area of Lehigh Acres. 1 acre lot, offering plenty of space for outdoor activities & privacy. Key Features: Spacious 4 bedrooms, perfect for families or guests. 2 modern bathrooms offering comfort & convenience. 2 car garage providing ample space for vehicles & storage. Enjoy clean, filtered water w/ the whole house reverse osmosis sys. Maintain a vibrant lawn w/ the installed sprinkler sys. Over built solar grid that supplies the house w/ 130% of needed electricity.  Beat the heat w/ the new AC sys. Outdoor entertainment area to relax & entertain guests, including a hot tub for ultimate relaxation. RV enthusiasts will appreciate the 50 amp hookup on the property. The kitchen has been beautifully renovated, featuring modern & stylish finishes. A shed, garden & chicken coop offer ample potential for storage & a self-sustaining lifestyle. Rest easy with a built-in security sys. The property has lots of potential for further development to meet your specific needs. Close proximity to River Hall & 30 min away from the beach. This home showcases a blend of comfort, style, & functionality.
